		<li data-target="#HomeCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
		<li data-target="#HomeCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
		<li data-target="#HomeCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
	</ol>

	<div class="carousel-inner">
		
		<div class="item active">
			<img src="http://hdwallpapersci.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/dsfsdf1.jpg" alt="Camping" class="img-responsive">
			<div class="carousel-caption">
				<h2>Because you deserve a weekend adventure completely off-the-grid</h2>
				<h4>Step 1 - Borrow a tent, bag, pad, pack</h4>
				<h4>Step 2 - Begin your epic journey!</h4>
		    </div>
		</div>

		<div class="item">
			<img src="http://www.wallsave.com/wallpapers/1920x1080/beachvolleyball/414822/beachvolleyball-beach-volleyball-serving-jump-hd-and-414822.jpg" alt="Volleyball" class="img-responsive">
			<div class="carousel-caption">
				<h2>Because a group of your friends are all free on a sunny Sunday</h2>
				<h4>Step 1 - Borrow a ball & net</h4>
				<h4>Step 2 - Head to the nearest beach!</h4>
		    </div>
		</div>

		<div class="item">
			<img src="http://img.wallpaperstock.net:81/beautiful-furniture-wallpapers_17618_1920x1080.jpg" alt="Home" class="img-responsive">
			<div class="carousel-caption">
				<h2>Because having something to show for the afternoon feels great</h2>
				<h4>Step 1 - Borrow some tools</h4>
				<h4>Step 2 - Recreate your world!</h4>
		    </div>
		</div>

		<div class="item">
			<img src="http://images5.alphacoders.com/313/313829.jpg" alt="Skiing" class="img-responsive">
			<div class="carousel-caption">
				<h2>Because it might be the closest you'll ever get to flying</h2>
				<h4>Step 1 - Borrow warm layers & protective gear</h4>
				<h4>Step 2 - Hit the slopes!</h4>
		    </div>
		</div>

	</div>
		
	<a class="left carousel-control" href="#HomeCarousel" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#HomeCarousel" data-slide="next">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
    </a>

</div>
</div>


